&lt;div class=&#34;paragraph&#34;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The &lt;em&gt;InvoiceJson&lt;/em&gt; class is a good example using most of the factory methods provided in the JSON conversion library.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;sect2&#34;&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;_tsv_mapping&#34;&gt;TSV Mapping&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;sect3&#34;&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&#34;_strengths_2&#34;&gt;Strengths&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;paragraph&#34;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The advantages of the Gleam TSV mapping library are:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;ulist&#34;&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Use POJO - &lt;em&gt;Plain Old Java Objects&lt;/em&gt; - and do not require Java Bean naming conventions for getters and setters.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Support immutable &lt;strong&gt;record&lt;/strong&gt; constructs of Java&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;imageblock&#34;&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;content&#34;&gt;
&lt;img src=&#34;../pics/tsv-class-diagram.svg&#34; alt=&#34;tsv class diagram&#34; width=&#34;474&#34; height=&#34;73&#34;/&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;paragraph&#34;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The TSV manipulation uses the &lt;a href=&#34;https://commons.apache.org/proper/commons-csv/&#34;&gt;apache commons csv&lt;/a&gt; library.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;sect3&#34;&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&#34;_recipes_2&#34;&gt;Recipes&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;paragraph&#34;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The classes provide factory methods to create JSON entity defining the transformation of a Java object to a JSON instance and vice-versa.
Below the code to map a bank connection object defined as a Java record with three String properties.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;listingblock&#34;&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;content&#34;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&#34;rouge highlight&#34; style=&#34;background-color: #f8f8f8&#34;&gt;&lt;code data-lang=&#34;java&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000;font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000;font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;static&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #445588;font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;TsvEntity&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000;font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #445588;font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;BankConnection&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000;font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #990000;font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;createTsvBankConnection&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000;font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;()&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color: #000000;font-weight: bold&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
